display_name: Apnea-Hypopnea Index (NREM): Apneas with no oxygen desaturation threshold used and with or without arousal+ hypopneas with > 30% flow reduction and with no oxygen desaturation threshold used and with or without arousal / hour of NREM sleep from type II polysomnography
description: Calculated - Summary metric of sleep disordered breathing events
calculation: 60 * ( hnrbp + hnrop + canbp + canop + oanbp + oanop ) / ( slpprdp - minremp )
